description: InstantaneousLicensing: Records of instantaneous licensing status for RAN cells, including timestamps, location, ID information, licensing mode, progress, administrative and operational states, and availability.  Columns describe the timestamp (dateTime), cell location (Area_Name, CellId, Id2, Id3, Id4), data type and format (vsDataType, vsDataFormatVersion), licensing details (InstantaneousLicensing.* columns), and unique identifiers (InstantaneousLicensing.instantaneousLicensingId, InstantaneousLicensing.swltId).
